      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know... people always say that. but the helplines dont actually change the fact that the person i built my whole life around is just gone. it just feels like i'm a ghost walking around in a body that doesnt belong to me anymore. it's not even a \"crisis\" anymore, it's just... the new reality. and it's empty. it's just totally empty.",
